response.overview: Peter Parker has been Spider-Man for eight years; at the ripe age of 23, he is about to see Wilson Fisk's empire crumble underneath his feet as the N.Y.P.D. can finally arrest 'The Kingpin' for years of political corruption and scandals. After successfully taking Fisk out, Peter's troubles start to unravel as a new threat rises to take Fisk's place: The Demons. New York starts falling into chaos, and Spider-Man's days may be numbered.
response.title: Marvel’s Spider-Man
